This is my "finish-the-night-off" place. Drinks are really cheap (can't remember the price, but it's about 300+ for 5 tequila shots), and they have outdoor seats for shisha. Services are close to non-existent and they never smile, but I didn't come here expecting flying services. I always come here half drunk, and take advantage of the cheap drinks and shisha to finish off. Lots of tourists in this area, which can be a good thing if you get talkative after getting hammered. Met some South African guys one time and we chatted all night - it was great fun.
The usher was super rude forcing us to leave with extremely aggressive manner. Will never come back here again!
Amazing place good food full of restourant.
